                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> When I came home from work I went out with a stale loaf to a customer—I went to look for my fellow-servant, but could not see him; I spent a shilling or two of my master's money; I met my fellow-servant, and he told me he and master had made it all up.</p>
